      "description": "This E46 M3 is powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing for a broad power band. Power is delivered via a 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox to an M-variable limited-slip differential, ensuring exceptional mechanical grip. The chassis has been maintained with a focus on longevity, including reinforced rear subframe mounting points and refreshed suspension bushings to maintain factory-spec kinematics. Recent service includes a cooling system overhaul and valve adjustment. A mechanically sound example that prioritizes driver engagement and longitudinal balance.",
