    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained 2018 Audi S4 in Daytona Gray Pearl. This vehicle has been my pride and joy, serving as a reliable and exhilarating daily driver. The exterior paint retains a deep, mirror-like shine, though I want to be transparent about a few minor stone chips on the front hood and a small scuff on the rear passenger wheel\u2014typical for a car that has been enjoyed on the open road. Inside, the Magma Red leather upholstery is in excellent shape with no tears or heavy bolsters wear; the cabin has been kept strictly smoke-free and the carbon fiber inlays are pristine. Every electronic feature, from the Virtual Cockpit to the Bang & Olufsen sound system, functions exactly as it should. Mechanically, the car is sound: it has a full service history with the most recent oil service and brake fluid flush completed just 1,500 miles ago. The tires have plenty of life left, and the transmission shifts smoothly through all gears. This is a complete, honest car ready for its next owner to get behind the wheel and drive.",
